{"tid":1341570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府 想將元朗 同 上環 撈埋一齊話暴徒？","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:55:02.000Z","uid":261448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"346da5b041065091c6bf45e2004a80c18ba2a33f","tid":1341570,"uid":261448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"Cctvb 又刻意無講元朗係咩人打 發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣搞輿論？<br />\n徹回又唔徹，政府唔聽民意，繼續玩依D把戲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm?fbclid=IwAR2z1PXoudY_IPbJaDOFuIIKXKaCk7hEfnLJjgnEjq8SZZJncT967a6wBvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F22%2FP2019072200010.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2z1PXoudY_IPbJaDOFuIIKXKaCk7hEfnLJjgnEjq8SZZJncT967a6wBvI&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=c189ac74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm?fbclid=IwAR2z1PXoudY_IPbJaDOFuIIKXKaCk7hEfnLJjgnEjq8SZZJncT967a6wBvI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府強烈譴責暴力行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　就昨日（七月二十一日）晚上在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為，特區政府作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　繼之前衝擊中聯辦大樓後，再有激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一帶向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，包括投擲汽油彈、縱火、擲磚，亦堵塞主要幹道，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n　　與此同時，在元朗有人聚眾在港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n　　香港作為法治社會完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，特區政府予以強烈譴責，並會嚴正追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月22日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時16分"},{"pid":"606a0f7c75adbf56cebaa2bf01d8609354a30660","tid":1341570,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d10660e32e29f60472f365de56c6c2b7f951d985","tid":1341570,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"我宣布「政警鄉黑」大合作，「黑警、黑鄉、黑社會」合稱「三黑」，必須追究「三黑」暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}